com.mattkinloch.softwareengineering

Class Listing

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.mattkinloch.softwareengineering.Listing

  • public class Listing
extends java.lang.Object
    A request created by an owner-user on the web app to have their pet sat, that can be seen and booked by sitter-users.
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    Matt Kinloch, Scott Guetens
